Log-Log4Cli

Lightweight perl logger for command line tools

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Log::Log4Cli

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Log-Log4Cli

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Log-Log4Cli

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Log-Log4Cli

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Log-Log4Cli/


